#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[smooth map between manifolds]

Let $f:M -> N$ be a map between #local("009D")[smooth manifolds] $M$ and $N$.
We say that $f$ is smooth if for all charts $phi$ of $M$ and $psi$ of $N$
the composition $phi @ f| @ psi^(-1)$ is a smooth map between subsets of $RR^n$.

